      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leek has softened, add the <strong>chopped potato[es] </strong>to the pot with your <strong>dried thyme </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
