    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[900ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 15-18 min or until the potato is fork-tender – this is your <strong>soup base</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1674830992858-x200.jpg",
