          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1674831001693-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato is fork tender, stir your <strong>blanched peas</strong> through the soup base with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong> – this is your <strong>pea soup</strong></p><p>Place the<strong> ciabatta halves</strong> in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
